description: When Jamie Steel happens upon a random Jeep out in the woods, he takes a closer look to make sure no one is in trouble. Turns out, Charlie Pattinson just decided to pull over on the trail and have himself a little nature session with himself. He's in his natural state, naked as a jaybird when Jamie happens by and catches a glimpse. Far from bashful, Charlie shows off his stick shift to Jamie and invites him to share in a little nature appreciation. Jamie doesn't need to be told twice, but he would be best to be well advised: Charlie's cock may be to Jamie's liking, but there's more to Charlie's plan than just a little forest bump & grind. If Jamie's not careful, he may find himself fucked in more ways than one! Enjoy!
title: Hit & Run
